@startuml US_4.1.3_SSD
autonumber

actor "Logistics\nOperator" as Operator
participant ":System" as System

== Search Plans ==
activate Operator
Operator -> System: Acede à secção "Operation Plans"
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta interface de pesquisa
deactivate System
Operator -> System: Introduz critérios de pesquisa (intervalo de datas, filtros)
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta lista de planos filtrados
deactivate System

== Sort Results ==
Operator -> System: Seleciona critério de ordenação
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta lista ordenada de planos
deactivate System

== View Plan Details ==
Operator -> System: Seleciona um plano da lista
activate System
System --> Operator: Apresenta detalhes do plano (operations, schedule, resources)
deactivate System
deactivate Operator

@enduml
